278
00:22:37,144 --> 00:22:41,296
<i>It calls for joint withdrawal</i>
<i>of all US and Soviet forces from Iran</i>

279
00:22:41,384 --> 00:22:42,737
<i>by noon on Sunday.</i>

280
00:22:42,824 --> 00:22:44,974
<i>However, NATO observers</i>
<i>in West Germany</i>

281
